Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.56,0:00:05.98,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1040,208)\c&H5886FC&}大家、是聯繫在一起的。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.75,0:00:03.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.83,0:00:04.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.46,0:00:05.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赤石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.38,0:00:05.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.08,0:00:06.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.21,0:00:09.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？天海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.92,0:00:11.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說 天海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.80,0:00:14.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.88,0:00:18.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了天海 你最近老是在發呆哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.14,0:00:21.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海同學 中午一起吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.94,0:02:09.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 小川同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.52,0:02:12.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有點事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.45,0:02:24.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說天海同學忘帶便當了？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.29,0:02:26.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近這段時間每天都是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.29,0:02:25.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}（不可以啊 天海同學！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.00,0:02:30.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}和富氫水來滿腹之後會吃壞肚子的）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.00,0:02:31.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在學校裡到處走 就像在找什麼一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們倒是吐槽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在努力調整氣氛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最開始我還以為她在開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}（我說你們聽到了嗎）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.97,0:02:38.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}（喂！）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.38,0:02:40.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}（我都說「喂」了！）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（天海同學真的失去靈感了呢）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.52,0:02:56.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些也是受那個的影響嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.69,0:03:00.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拍不到靈異照片什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靈的氣息也消失什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.32,0:03:08.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代答武士和小太妹其實就在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.08,0:03:14.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是好事嗎 之前都太吵鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你嘴上這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上你看不到奶奶了應該很寂寞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.43,0:03:27.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奶奶在的！就算看不見也會守護著我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.35,0:03:31.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.69,0:03:35.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼 只是覺得井上同學變了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.77,0:03:41.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是啊 之前只會一個勁地說靈是不存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.95,0:03:44.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 要這麼說的話我們也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.66,0:03:44.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明完全就和平常一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.95,0:03:51.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卻覺得學校和街上都有點太安靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.92,0:03:54.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海沒有告訴我們的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們都不會注意到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是我們看不見而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實際上有很多有趣的傢伙存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也很有趣哦~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全都多虧了天海同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又被無視了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多虧了天海嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許確實是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到那傢伙那樣笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總覺得有點難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.29,0:04:40.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 聽說天海倒下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噓 保健室要肅靜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼異常的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想大概是勞累過度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:53.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勞累麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,監護人很快就會來接她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們幾個就快點回教室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勞累果然是因為那個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 也只有那個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.62,0:05:10.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼對我不會有些過分麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}不准偷看女孩子的睡顏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大…大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.17,0:05:25.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底去哪兒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我看看你們的臉 聽聽你們的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求…你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的話就在這裡哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來不是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在夢裡也見不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海請假了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟昨天都累倒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也只能這樣了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 放學後我們一起去探望天海吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贊成 井上同學也會去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.79,0:06:01.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？嗯……嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 明明你們還特意來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.13,0:06:10.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 見不了天海是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.05,0:06:13.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身體狀況有這麼不好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.56,0:06:17.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有 醫生也說只是勞累過度而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她現在在自己的房間裡休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.48,0:06:23.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…那到底是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.49,0:06:31.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你們這麼擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己沒臉見你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那算什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.13,0:06:44.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明沒有拜託過她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她卻老是擔心別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.76,0:06:51.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開什麼玩笑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.39,0:06:57.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上同學 我覺得響自己也是明白這點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.10,0:07:03.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 因為看不見一直在身邊的靈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以她不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不知道該跟她說些什麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.36,0:07:16.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實這幾天響都沒有好好吃飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她沒吃飯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是從七夕之後開始的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這之後體力會越來越不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.55,0:07:30.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 我們就先回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.72,0:07:33.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海就拜託您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊啊 總覺得有點不甘心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們什麼都沒辦法為她做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.98,0:07:48.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果能想辦法幫天海同學取回靈感就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.19,0:07:51.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,取回靈感什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,普通的高中生做得到才怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有她不吃飯這點也讓人在意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.49,0:08:01.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 這個可能才是最嚴重的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.04,0:08:06.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 我說井上 你之前說的表弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說的勇氣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.09,0:08:10.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙吃飯很挑剔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你和天海一起做飯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這又怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.22,0:08:17.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我只是想如果做相同的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海會不會吃飯什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.64,0:08:24.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒可能的 因為那是天海告訴了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對勇氣而言的重要的料理是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過這個真的很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喜歡的話我也很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.32,0:08:36.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是……非常重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.79,0:08:41.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 井上同學？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 我有點事 你們先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.88,0:08:47.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-誒？   -嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.63,0:08:52.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了 請問是誰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上同學？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.64,0:08:59.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 跑那麼急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是忘了什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.73,0:09:04.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有事想拜託您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.41,0:09:19.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.45,0:09:23.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉 咱們想到一塊去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為沒辦法為天海做些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.42,0:09:31.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只能幫天海做她現在做不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海苔燒蛋送了！給！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.26,0:09:37.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就大家一起收拾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.09,0:09:40.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其他還有很多地方要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.69,0:09:55.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有人在背後鼓勵著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代答武士和小太妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有很多天海的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.95,0:10:05.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.62,0:10:07.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算我不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海也結下了很多的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.75,0:10:13.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我重要的朋友們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是全部都失去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全因為我的任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,羈絆已經瓦解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海 你趕快給我出來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？誒 井上同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.92,0:10:56.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,臉色這麼差 給我好好吃飯增加體力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.88,0:10:57.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.05,0:10:58.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.09,0:11:03.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家總是一臉幸福地吃著貢品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這會讓我非常的高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.56,0:11:17.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在已經只能在記憶裡見到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 只有我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別說廢話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點吃！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.42,0:11:39.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 好好嚼嚼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.11,0:12:00.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在想這會不會就是你現在想吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前你給勇氣做的雞蛋燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.37,0:12:18.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個是你媽媽留下的做法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.67,0:12:22.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直想著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不可以吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼可以只有我能吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.26,0:12:29.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.98,0:12:38.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.44,0:12:41.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是當然的！你可是活著的啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些傢伙肯定也是這麼想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.25,0:13:02.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直覺得這份感情不是單方面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:08.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活著的人也好 死去的人也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:10.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們的心情是連在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而能夠確認這份朕系的 就是我的靈感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.31,0:13:21.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 我看不到大家 也聽不到他們的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.44,0:13:26.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想都沒想過失去靈感的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去了重要的羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.33,0:13:35.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這之後我要以怎樣的面目活下去才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.04,0:13:38.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好怕 好不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才一直把自己關著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.88,0:13:43.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不和我們見面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想再給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.14,0:13:51.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能和井上同學你們當好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是多虧了靈感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有靈感的我 一無所有的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使如此也能維繫著羈絆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.02,0:14:01.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有這種自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.61,0:14:07.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要走了哦 天海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 去哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有想讓你見見的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請等等 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.66,0:14:21.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉啊天海 我現在快氣炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.09,0:14:28.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去了就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 井上同學和天海同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒 守屋老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.06,0:14:40.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.19,0:14:44.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 聽說你昨天請假了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起來恢復健康了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.44,0:14:48.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是絕對不可以勉強自己哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老師是要出門嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:56.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要去報告一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恭喜您！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我之前一直沒有 去往和那孩子一起生活過的地方見她的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個孩子來見我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得這次該輪到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.43,0:15:19.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多虧了你哦 天海同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.40,0:15:23.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯 因為你再一次把我們聯繫上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那孩子也會開心的 一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.78,0:15:33.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小響？果然是小響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.12,0:15:44.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近沒在超市看到你 我擔心了好久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓您費心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和朋友一起來買東西？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們家今天要做土豆燉肉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.72,0:15:56.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從那之後 時不時有種女兒回家了的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.22,0:15:58.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小太妹小姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.77,0:16:01.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我做飯都不敢偷工減料了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是頭疼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.27,0:16:06.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你 小響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.20,0:16:15.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.41,0:16:22.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖說我和他非親非故 不過…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.25,0:16:23.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.21,0:16:27.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是心血來潮而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.71,0:16:29.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起這個 小女孩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不夠精神啊 你還年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以給我打起精神來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,（去吃點那種難吃的巧克力什麼的吧）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.51,0:16:41.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 井上同學說的想讓我見見的人就是他們？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.98,0:16:44.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 真的全都是偶然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.65,0:16:48.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 多虧了這些你也稍微明白點了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.23,0:16:49.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成美！響！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像來了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.90,0:16:55.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.74,0:16:59.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近還好麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勇氣 好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.91,0:17:05.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說這是你妹妹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 長大了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.34,0:17:10.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然叫你出來麻煩你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.05,0:17:15.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼 我也想讓響見見響歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.05,0:17:17.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是叫響歌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像這樣正式地說話還是第一次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫天海響…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響歌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.65,0:17:29.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,寫作響亮的歌聲的響歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說是從你名字裡取的字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.98,0:17:33.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候沒能好好說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:42.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多虧了響 我成了個好哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.04,0:17:47.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,口…向…響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.12,0:17:48.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說 剛才是不是說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.29,0:17:53.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 響歌好厲害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有我說了雞蛋燒難吃 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.39,0:18:05.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實是非常好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是好好地聯繫在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勇氣也好 大家也好 都很重視你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還打算說靈感什麼的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.36,0:18:22.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 我除此之外什麼都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.03,0:18:26.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別說傻話了 全都是你聯繫起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然一開始可能確實是因為靈感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.17,0:18:35.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是把人們和靈聯繫起來的不是別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.92,0:18:36.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是一個叫天海響的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愛管閒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.97,0:18:42.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,溫柔的老好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是這樣的一個你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.06,0:18:50.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我到現在還是會害怕得不得了 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想和你永遠做朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.65,0:18:58.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上同學 可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.82,0:19:02.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我們彼此相連…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是當然的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.16,0:19:09.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你再稍微任性點也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果這被允許的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.33,0:19:14.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想和井上同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你們聯繫在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.26,0:19:18.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想和各位靈聯繫在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使我無法看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.40,0:19:36.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喲 響妹子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海醬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 臉色很糟糕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:50.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就趕緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我看看你們的胖次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.54,0:19:57.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 雖然我明白你們高興的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.21,0:20:02.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下們從今以後也想一直陪在你身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.01,0:20:03.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.43,0:20:13.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來我也早就和你們聯繫上了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊！天海同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 打起精神了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上就熱鬧起來了比什麼都好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.49,0:20:24.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 就是得這樣才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 一定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.58,0:20:34.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管有沒有靈感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.87,0:20:36.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的響都和大家聯繫在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們都願意待在我身邊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都願意和我聯繫在一起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.53,0:21:02.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算看不見也請不要哭泣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.95,0:21:08.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算看不見也請不要悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,溫柔的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,溫暖的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,憐愛的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是每個人都有的和某個人的聯繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.46,0:21:25.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也守護在我們的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.51,0:21:34.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若不安之時來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.35,0:21:36.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就伸出手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.06,0:21:39.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼做的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.66,0:21:55.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果可以的話能和我說說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.87,0:21:57.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.27,0:23:42.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然發生了很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.81,0:23:45.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是又能和大家在一起生活我很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.15,0:23:48.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海同學 快點快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.57,0:23:50.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都準備好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.57,0:23:52.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.45,0:23:54.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 遊樂園又不會逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.87,0:23:57.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不如說井上更可能逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.49,0:23:59.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟遊樂園有那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.45,0:24:00.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵 吵死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.21,0:24:04.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Re-Kan！最終回「這是夏天的回憶」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.67,0:24:08.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,願這一天也能成為美好的羈絆

